This is the notes for LogicalQueryOperators

We have 2 logical query operators:
or 
and

What if we wanted to get the courses published by an author or get the courses that are published
This is where the or operator comes into play 

the and operator works just like the find method with all the filters we have inside of in it 

I think these 2 operators work just like we use them for if statements (||, &&)